                                                            -To facilitate the tailoring of online advertising to your interests.
                                                            <br> <br></p>
                                                            
                                                            <h6><span class="headline">What type of cookies does afriexpressglobal use?</span></h6>
                                                            <p>
                                                            Cookies can either be session cookies or persistent cookies. A session cookie expires automatically when you close your browser. A persistent cookie will remain until it expires or you delete your cookies. Expiration dates are set in the cookies themselves; some may expire after a few minutes while others
                                                             may expire after multiple years. Cookies placed by the website you’re visiting are called “first party cookies”.
